OL,5, Indian agency workers hired to replace 
OL,6, P&O Ferries crews in Dover are being   
OL,7, paid #1.81 an hour, a union claims.    
OL,9,FThe Rail, Maritime and Transport union 
OL,10,F(RMT) said the low pay was a "shocking 
OL,11,Fexploitation" and "a betrayal of those 
OL,12,Fwho have been sacked".                 
OL,14,FP&O said the figure was inaccurate but 
OL,15,Fsaid it could not comment on how much  
OL,16,Fagencies pay workers on ferries.       
OL,18,FSome of P&O's ferries are registered in
OL,19,FCyprus, meaning they do not have to pay
OL,20,Fthe minimum wage required by UK law.   
